So, if we run "pkg_add -t /tmp/SOMEXXXXX.tmp package" pkg_add will check /tmp/SOMEXXXXX.tmp
for existance and then completly ignore -t parametr instead of create /tmp/SOME<UNIQNUM>.tmp directory

